	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Proposed a bill to fill priesthoods by popular election (see above, on Laelius); and instituted the practice of addressing the people in the Forum directly (Cic. Lael. 96; cf. Varro RR 1.2.9; Plut. CG 5.3; cf. Grueber, CRRBM 2.274; Cesano, Stud. Num. 1.211f.)." .
